quran[29{c,v,t}:
70,11,halaank woh aik dosray ko dukhaay jayen ge mujrim chahay ga ke is din ke azaab se bachney ke liye apni aulaad ko
70,12,"apni biwi ko, apne bhai ko"
70,13,apne qareeb tareen khandan ko jo usay panah dainay wala tha
70,14,aur roye zameen ke sab logon ko Fidya mein daiday aur yeh tadbeer ussay nijaat dila day
70,15,hargiz nahi woh to bharakti hui aag ki lapat hogi
70,16,jo gosht post ko chaat jaye gi
70,17,pukaar pukaar kar apni taraf bulaye gi har uss shakhs ko jis ne haq se mun morra aur peeth pheri
70,18,aur maal jama kya aur saint saintkar rakha
70,19,ensaan tharrdalla peda kya gaya hai
70,20,jab is par museebat aati hai to ghabra uthta hai
70,21,aur jab usay khushhali naseeb hoti hai to bukhal karne lagta hai
70,22,magar woh log ( iss aib se bachay hue hain ) jo namaz parhnay walay hain
70,23,jo apni namaz ki hamesha pabandi karte hain
70,24,"jin ke malon mein ,"
70,25,sayel aur mahroom ka aik haq muqarrar hai
70,26,jo roz jaza ko barhaq mantay hain
70,27,jo apne rab ke azaab se drtay hain
70,28,kyunkay unn ke rab ka azaab aisi cheez nahi hai jis se koi be khauf ho
70,29,jo apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karte hain
70,30,bajuz apni biwion ya apni mamloka aurton ke jin se mehfooz nah rakhnay mein un par koi malamat nahi
70,31,Albata jo is ke ilawa kuch aur chahain wohi hadd se tajawaz karne walay hain
70,32,jo apni amanaton ki hifazat aur apne ehad ka paas karte hain
70,33,jo apni gwahyon mein raast baazi par qaim rehtay hain
70,34,aur jo apni namaz ki hifazat karte hain
70,35,yeh log izzat ke sath jannat ke baghoon mein rahen ge
70,36,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kya baat hai ke yeh munkareen dayen aur baen se ,"
70,37,giroh Dur giroh tumhari taraf doray chalay aa rahay hain ?
70,38,kya inn mein se har aik yeh lalach rakhta hai ke woh Nemat bhari jannat mein daakhil kar diya jaye ga ?
70,39,hargiz nahi hum ne jis cheez se inn ko peda kya hai ussay yeh khud jantay hain
